		"description": "<p>Your mutations elicit morbid fascination in those around you. Once per long rest, as a bonus action you may choose one creature that you can see within 15 feet of you. That creature must make a Charisma saving throw versus your maneuver DC or become fixated by you until the end of your next turn. Once you have used this ability, you may not do so again until you complete a short or a long rest.</p>\n<p>You may use your Otherwordly Curiosity feature as a free action if you are frenzied.</p>",
